OL,3,CDad's 'difficult decision' to close
OL,4,Cice-cream parlour in honour of son, 7
OL,6,FThe father of a seven-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fwas killed in a hit and run accident
OL,8,Fin Folkestone, says he's taken the
OL,9,F"difficult decision" to close a
OL,10,Fdessert parlour created in his honour.
OL,12,FWilliam Brown Junior was knocked over
OL,13,Fby a van when he ran into Sandgate
OL,14,FEsplanade when trying to retrieve his
OL,15,Ffootball on 6 December 2023.
OL,17,FThe driver of the car, Stewart Powell,
OL,18,Fwas sentenced to 14 weeks in prison,
OL,19,Fsuspended for 12 months - and banned
OL,20,Ffrom driving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
