OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773497487
OL,3,CDad's 'difficult decision' to close
OL,4,Cice-cream parlour in honour of son, 7
OL,6,FWilliam's father, William Brown Snr,
OL,7,Fopened the ice-cream parlour on
OL,8,FSandgate Road, a few months after his
OL,9,Fson's death, to support his campaign
OL,10,Fto teach children about road safety.
OL,12,FCalled Will Brown Junior's, the
OL,13,Fparlour is decorated with murals, some
OL,14,Fshowing William.
OL,16,FBut the parlour has now been closed.
OL,18,FPosting on social media, Mr Brown
OL,19,Fsaid: "I have made the difficult
OL,20,Fdecision to close Will Brown Jr's.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773497487
OL,3,CDad's 'difficult decision' to close
OL,4,Cice-cream parlour in honour of son, 7
OL,6,F"I would like to express my gratitude
OL,7,Fto all who supported the shop and
OL,8,Findeed myself through my journey of
OL,9,Fgrief.
OL,11,F"Will Brown Jr's became a safe haven
OL,12,Ffor many, ignited that inner joy to
OL,13,Fall, donated thousands to local clubs
OL,14,Fand charities, as well as most
OL,15,Fcritically spreading the message of
OL,16,Froad safety.
OL,18,F"This gives me an incredible amount of
OL,19,Fpeace and comfort in making this
OL,20,Fdecision.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773497487
OL,3,CDad's 'difficult decision' to close
OL,4,Cice-cream parlour in honour of son, 7
OL,6,F"Will Brown Jr's was my outlet for my
OL,7,Fgrieving process all while honouring
OL,8,Fmy son, William lan Brown. I will
OL,9,Fforever remain proud of that process,
OL,10,Fproud of myself and inconceivably
OL,11,Fproud of my son.
OL,13,F"Again, thank you for your support
OL,14,Fthrough this chapter, it is eternally
OL,15,Fappreciated and never forgotten."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
